    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2008 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the iconic S65 4.0L V8 engine. This high-revving, naturally aspirated powerplant utilizes eight individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio to deliver 414hp at an 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis remains rigid, supported by M-specific suspension geometry and an M Variable Differential Lock that ensures precise torque distribution across the rear axle. This unit is a well-maintained driver\u2019s car; while the aesthetic shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical vitals are robust. The VANOS system is quiet, and the gear synchronization remains sharp. This is a mechanically sound performance machine for those who prioritize longitudinal and lateral dynamics over a showroom finish.",
