    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a well-maintained 2018 Executive Sport Sedan finished in a sophisticated Midnight Blue Metallic. This vehicle has been driven thoughtfully and remains in solid mechanical and aesthetic shape. The exterior maintains a high-gloss finish, with only minor cosmetic imperfections consistent with regular use, such as light stone chipping on the front hood and a small scuff on the passenger-side mirror housing. Inside, the premium charcoal leather upholstery is free of rips or stains, and the cabin remains a strictly non-smoking environment. All electronic components\u2014including the dual-zone climate control, touchscreen navigation, and 12-speaker audio system\u2014are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no leaks or warning lights. We have kept a comprehensive folder of service records, including a recent multi-point inspection, fresh oil service, and a cooling system flush performed within the last 3,000 miles. The tires are matching sets with plenty of tread depth remaining for several seasons. This is a reliable, honest vehicle that offers a premium driving experience without the new-car price tag.",
